items.title: Snap reactions to every Week 17 game: Broncos stay in control of AFC destiny; Cowboys, Vikings win
items.description: Our NFL Nation reporters answer big questions from each Week 17 game. Here's what you need to know.

items.title: Vikes dominate Lions despite woeful passing game
items.description: The Vikings accomplished the rare feat of winning an NFL game while finishing with fewer than 10 net passing yards.

items.title: Lions' playoff chances end with loss: 'It sucks'
items.description: The Lions officially fell out of playoff contention with a 23-10 loss to the Vikings, leaving Detroit to evaluate how it needs to improve.
